---
layout: base.njk
title: The Munder Difflin Blog
description: "Guides, deep dives, and comparisons on running multi-agent Claude Code: orchestration, agent memory, automation, and the tooling landscape."
seoTitle: "Multi-agent & Claude Code blog — Munder Difflin"
permalink: /index.html
---
{% block head %}
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Blog",
  "name": "{{ site.blogName }}",
  "description": {{ site.description | dump | safe }},
  "url": "{{ site.baseUrl }}",
  "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "Munder Difflin", "logo": { "@type": "ImageObject", "url": "{{ site.origin }}/logo.png" } }
}
</script>
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "{{ site.origin }}/" },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Blog", "item": "{{ site.baseUrl }}" }
  ]
}
</script>
{% endblock %}
{% block content %}
{%- set posts = collections.posts -%}
<header class="page-head wrap">
  <p class="eyebrow">Notes from the office floor</p>
  <h1>The Munder Difflin <span class="hl">Blog.</span></h1>
  <p class="lead">Guides, deep dives, and comparisons on running <strong>multi-agent Claude
  Code</strong> — orchestration, agent memory, automation, and the tooling landscape. From the team
  building a self-coordinating hive of agents with a GOD orchestrator you talk to.</p>

  <div class="filters" role="navigation" aria-label="Topics">
    <a class="chip" aria-current="page">All<span class="ct">{{ posts.length }}</span></a>
    {% for c in collections.categories %}
    <a class="chip" href="{{ ('/topics/' + c.slug + '/') | u }}">{{ c.name }}<span class="ct">{{ c.posts.length }}</span></a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</header>

{% if posts.length %}
<div class="wrap featured">
  {%- set p = posts[0] -%}
  {% include "card.njk" %}
</div>

{% if posts.length > 1 %}
<section class="wrap">
  <div class="post-grid">
    {% for p in posts %}{% if not loop.first %}{% include "card.njk" %}{% endif %}{% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}
{% else %}
<div class="center-stage wrap">
  <div>
    <p class="eyebrow">Coming soon</p>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(28px,5vw,44px)">The first dispatch is in the oven.</h1>
    <p>New posts land here. Subscribe via <a href="{{ site.baseUrl }}feed.xml">RSS</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>
{% endif %}
{% endblock %}
